title: Kwanruetai
overview: Chatklao started his work as a doctor for a hospital in camp to pay the loan back. He meets Kwanruetaiwho has always teased him. However, he finds himself in love with her. She is the daughter of Maratee and general Pinij who left nothing for her and mother after death. Maratee doesn't love her because of this. Kwanruetai really hates Chatklao because she was told that her family was brought down because of Juthathep family.
